>It is impossible to authenticate the person on the other end of the
>connection unless the two of you share a secret....

Not necessarily so.  Authentication could be through a mutually-trusted
3rd party.  Or, if you had multiple paths that you somehow knew did lead
to the person on the other end, not all of which are corruptible.

